---
// Floating "buy me a beer" button. Hidden on print via .no-print.
---

<a
  href="https://buymeacoffee.com/cmaddocks"
  target="_blank"
  rel="noopener noreferrer"
  class="no-print fixed bottom-5 right-5 z-50 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap rounded-full border-2 border-[#0d1b2a] bg-[#FFDD00] px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold !text-[#0d1b2a] no-underline shadow-[0_2px_0_#0d1b2a,0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,.15)] transition hover:-translate-y-px hover:shadow-[0_3px_0_#0d1b2a,0_6px_14px_rgba(0,0,0,.2)] hover:!no-underline"
  title="If this tool saved you time, you can say thanks"
>
  🍺 Buy me a beer
</a>
